e current heading. The heading indicator represents the direction the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"device is facing, which is sized according to the reported accuracy."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithHeading"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserTrackingMode/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnusertrackingmode\/mlnusertrackingmodefollowwithcourse","abstract":[{"text":"The map follows the user location and rotates when the course changes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Course represents the direction in which the device is traveling.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The default user location annotation shows a puck-shaped indicator","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that rotates as the course changes.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" object from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"userLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property of the map view displayed in your application.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNUserLocation","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"require the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotations."}]}}}